RGB to YUV tool

Description:

	RGB to YUV tool is used to modify an image with RGB format to YUV format 


Compilation:
	1. Run autoreconf -iv
	2. Run ./configure --host=arm-linux-gnueabi 
	3. Run Make

	The binary is stored under src/


Execution:
	rgb2yuv_neon must be executed from src/

	Valid arguments:                                               
	 -a: displays the information of the author of the program.    
	 -h: displays this help menu                                   
	 -i: RGBfile specifies the RGB file to be converted.           
	 -o: YUVfile specifies the output file name.                   

Command lines Examples:
        ./rgb2yuv_neon -i image.rgb -o image.yuv
